{"tid":1404501,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[買罩注意2] 面罩及配件合理價格範圍資，小心比人劏","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:46:00.000Z","uid":48872,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b102b494bc7d656edcbb0267283996c06791f43e","tid":1404501,"uid":48872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"上一個post講過有鋪頭食人血饅頭亦都有唔巴絲分享被劏經過，哩個post講吓啲價位大致點先叫正常，巴打絲打小心啲，如果有得揀就唔好硬食人血饅頭價，因為多咗出嚟嘅錢隨時夠你買多set比你身邊嗰個，貨比三家好緊要，大家嘅血汗錢嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[買罩注意]新填地華泰行安全用品正仆街食人血饅頭 3m502<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1336576\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1336576</a><br />\n<br />\n要留意對付龍煙只有幾個組合ok，所以講嘅價格都會根據返<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1kCKI6LBgGl01IJz9arT2JvefJnpyNF0XZ6PL5fwEjl0/htmlview#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1kCKI6LBgGl01IJz9arT2JvefJnpyNF0XZ6PL5fwEjl0%2Fhtmlview%23&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=c790aa05\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1kCKI6LBgGl01IJz9arT2JvefJnpyNF0XZ6PL5fwEjl0/htmlview#</a><br />\n香城online 裝備手冊提及過有效嘅裝備，入面都有介紹唔同組合嘅強度，多謝一眾巴絲咁努力整出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n所謂合理價格會綜合amazon、五金街同我個人經驗約略定吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能攻略都有提及價位，但希望呢個post可以更加方便你地同提供更多價格。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3M:<br />\n罩：<br />\n7500系列：<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/MGimKOMN_DQpFkD7TedTTgzFkUY68u1JynffvPuuO-f9c_hYBkhiSMycICt2dKDTqIFBurM7g1nZbdoojufeVVGrujGVMiRFEZkwJE9a7v16rGDpKaMqZ0dz_LvQzwgm1zrWUknIRg=w281-h193\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh6.googleusercontent.com%2FMGimKOMN_DQpFkD7TedTTgzFkUY68u1JynffvPuuO-f9c_hYBkhiSMycICt2dKDTqIFBurM7g1nZbdoojufeVVGrujGVMiRFEZkwJE9a7v16rGDpKaMqZ0dz_LvQzwgm1zrWUknIRg%3Dw281-h193&h=d6590579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">180$-220$</span><br />\n<br />\n6500系列：<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61mEzQH02BL._SX342_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61mEzQH02BL._SX342_.jpg&h=d514fc24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">200$-220$</span><br />\n<br />\n3200系列:<br />\n<img src=\"https://mall.builderhood.com/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/18e2eb1d062708aed8a3f1bdae4edc86/3/2/3200-single-cartridge-respirator_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmall.builderhood.com%2Fpub%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F18e2eb1d062708aed8a3f1bdae4edc86%2F3%2F2%2F3200-single-cartridge-respirator_1.jpg&h=c0a71c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">90$-120$</span><br />\n<br />\n盒:<br />\n<br />\n3311k (多數同3200罩一齊買)<br />\n<img src=\"https://mall.builderhood.com/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/7bbb72c0794a654c24debf7883dbeecb/3/m/3m_3311k-55_55cc_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmall.builderhood.com%2Fpub%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F7bbb72c0794a654c24debf7883dbeecb%2F3%2Fm%2F3m_3311k-55_55cc_.jpg&h=65b4f036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">38$-50$</span><br />\n<br />\n以下盒都係同7500及6500系列<span style=\"color: red;\">罩</span>用<br />\n<br />\n6092X 系列<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">150$-170$</span>一對<br />\n<br />\n600X 系列<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">80$-110$</span>一對<br />\n<br />\n棉系列<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係買p100standard唔好買錯，因為龍煙主要係啲particles 搞到你口水鼻涕一齊流。<br />\n<br />\n有P100 standard嘅棉有：<br />\n2097/2096/2091<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">20$-35$</span>一對<br />\n<br />\n6092x系列嘅盒就已經有埋P100嘅棉喺個盒入面，唔洗買多個棉。<br />\n<br />\n但如果你只能買到600x盒，你就要買多個502轉接膠蓋用嚟接駁P100 standard嘅棉落個600X盒到。<br />\n<br />\n502: (千祈唔好比人水咗買501或太心急當咗501同502差唔多就買。)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/fa8c3b21-1b89-45a3-8e60-e89db4dd0070_1.c77e9f00f066c1f3a90e202bc155b796.jpeg?odnHeight=450&amp;odnWidth=450&amp;odnBg=FFFFFF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi5.walmartimages.com%2Fasr%2Ffa8c3b21-1b89-45a3-8e60-e89db4dd0070_1.c77e9f00f066c1f3a90e202bc155b796.jpeg%3FodnHeight%3D450%26odnWidth%3D450%26odnBg%3DFFFFFF&h=2ce9e83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">35$-60$</span>一對。<br />\n<br />\n巴絲打們嘅錢一定要用得其所先至可以慢慢發夢，更有效率。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我嘅價唔一定最合理，最平。希望你地會補充，睇見啲小朋友飯都冇得食買晒裝備就好心痛。<br />\n<br />\n而家amazon 訂一set 6502+60923連運費都要成五舊幾，所以香港本地搵到良心鋪買可以慳唔少。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝武運昌隆，我地嘅努力一定可以光復香港。"},{"pid":"15387f0ed4529a819f377a9f3e3ab6f61379ac5f","tid":1404501,"uid":48872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:52:50.000Z","msg":"推，買還買，唔好比人劏，有時間就唔好急。"},{"pid":"e53412593c9fe6979e7772f2aef39601acc2d9b9","tid":1404501,"uid":48872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"推，買還買，唔好比人劏，有時間就唔好急。"},{"pid":"01338af17e76164cd279c0d89f0e918aa431dfc6","tid":1404501,"uid":48872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:19:27.000Z","msg":"推到個個都平價入手，慳得一蚊得一蚊"},{"pid":"6c2b492e671c2d9bd6a64ebb37e71327d49a4a41","tid":1404501,"uid":48872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"推到個個都平價入手，慳得一蚊得一蚊"},{"pid":"fecc048c46fcd7b2684330562090595b87494560","tid":1404501,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"實用post必推<br />\n<br />\n頭盔方面可以買open face，就用到豬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵到有門店試size嘅鋪有賣平價電單車頭盔，大家可以參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.leelik.hk/categories/helmet?sort_by=lowest_price&amp;order_by=asc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.leelik.hk%2Fcategories%2Fhelmet%3Fsort_by%3Dlowest_price%26order_by%3Dasc&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg